{"id":57,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":57,"title":"D&C 53","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 53"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to Algernon Sidney Gilbert, at Kirtland, Ohio, June 8, 1831. At Sidney Gilbert’s request, the Prophet inquired of the Lord as to Brother Gilbert’s work and appointment in the Church."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.1-3"},"1–3"],", Sidney Gilbert’s calling and election in the Church is to be ordained an elder;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.4-7"},"4–7"],", He is also to serve as a bishop’s agent."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.1","order":"06.05.053.6642"},["b","1"],"Behold, I say unto you, my servant Sidney Gilbert, that I have heard your prayers; and you have called upon me that it should be made known unto you, of the Lord your God, concerning your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"calling"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"election"],"in the church, which I, the Lord, have raised up in these last days."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.2","order":"06.05.053.6643"},["b","2"],"Behold, I, the Lord, who was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"crucified"],"for the sins of the world, give unto you a commandment that you shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"forsake"],"the world."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.3","order":"06.05.053.6644"},["b","3"],"Take upon you mine ordination, even that of an elder, to preach faith and repentance and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"remission"],"of sins, according to my word, and the reception of the Holy Spirit by the laying on of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"hands"],";"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.4","order":"06.05.053.6645"},["b","4"],"And also to be an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"agent"],"unto this church in the place which shall be appointed by the bishop, according to commandments which shall be given hereafter."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.5","order":"06.05.053.6646"},["b","5"],"And again, verily I say unto you, you shall take your journey with my servants Joseph Smith, Jun., and Sidney Rigdon."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.6","order":"06.05.053.6647"},["b","6"],"Behold, these are the first ordinances which you shall receive; and the residue shall be made known in a time to come, according to your labor in my vineyard."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.7","order":"06.05.053.6648"},["b","7"],"And again, I would that ye should learn that he only is saved who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"endureth"],"unto the end. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.1a","order":"06.05.053.6649"},["b","1a"],"Compare with",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/12"},"sections 12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14"},"14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/15"},"15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/16"},"16"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.1b","order":"06.05.053.6651"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/election"},"TG Election"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.2a","order":"06.05.053.6653"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-crucifixion-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Crucifixion of"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.2b","order":"06.05.053.6655"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/6.17"},"2 Cor. 6:17"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world"},"TG World"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worldliness"},"Worldliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.3a","order":"06.05.053.6657"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/remission-of-sins"},"TG Remission of Sins"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.3b","order":"06.05.053.6659"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hands-laying-on-of"},"TG Hands, Laying on of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.4a","order":"06.05.053.6661"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/57.6.6-15"},"D&C 57:6 (6–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.113"},"84:113"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/53.7a","order":"06.05.053.6663"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.22"},"Matt. 10:22"],"."]]}
